frames.caption: A cozy log cabin is nestled in a snowy forest, with warm light glowing from its windows. Smoke gently rises from the chimney, blending into the starry night sky illuminated by the northern lights. Snow-covered trees surround the cabin, creating a serene winter scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a tranquil winter setting with a log cabin surrounded by snow-laden trees. The northern lights add a magical touch to the night sky, while the warm glow from the cabin suggests comfort and warmth amidst the cold.
